reviewText: Have been searching for this movie for ages.. looking under Belinda only realising it went under another title of midnite dancer Enjoyed the movie when it first came out and still enjoyed today. A kings cross of the past.. a tiny bit of Rickey May who I have seen in real life and was a great proformer( was knowen to eat a whole leg of roast lamb for dinner)Belinda is so innocent and beautiful and her eyes are opened up in the harsh world of the show girlMidnight Dancer [VHS]
